snippet.title: Dr. Samaria M Colbert
snippet.description:
Dr. Samaria Maria Colbert is a anointed writer, licensed therapist, speaker and entrepreneur.  Samaria also has a heart to counsel she is the founder and CEO of Kingdom Creative Counseling PLLC. The counseling part of her private practice is dedicated to helping individuals and recover from abuse,  depression and anxiety.   Samaria uses an integrative approach to therapy that includes, traditional mental health strategies , inner healing, and Christian counseling. Samaria also  counsels, trains and develops  ministry and business leaders.

Samaria has written and published over 55 books.

PO BOX 78112
Greensboro NC 27427

To request her to speak at one of your events or other business inquiries visit the website and completed the contact form, 
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FA...

Other business inquiries: drsamariacolbert@gmail.com

For MH counseling, you must be a NC resident visit the website www.kingdomcreativecounseling.com. Email inquiries will not be responded to.
